    korthoR.Rmd

    Abstract

    korthoR calculates pairwise kmer jaccard distance between all sequences of a AAStringSet

    Introduction

    Installation

    To install this package, start R (version “4.3.2”) and enter:

    if (!requireNamespace("BiocManager", quietly = TRUE))
    install.packages("BiocManager")

BiocManager::install(
    c(
    "MSA2dist")
)

devtools::install_github("kullrich/korthoR", build_vignettes = TRUE, dependencies = TRUE)

    Load korthoR 

    # load korthoR
library(korthoR)
# load example data
data(hiv, package="MSA2dist")

    Count kmers of length 6 for all amino acids 

    l <- hiv |>
    MSA2dist::cds2aa() |>
    korthoR::count_kmers(k=6)
    ##
